items.title: Wall Street Analysts Look Bullish on Home Depot (HD): Should You Buy?
items.description: The average brokerage recommendation (ABR) for Home Depot (HD) is equivalent to a Buy. The overly optimistic recommendations of Wall Street analysts make the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric questionable. So, is it worth buying the stock?
